data.title: TV Schedule for WIVM-LD Newcomerstown, OH
data.meta_description: Check out today's TV schedule for WIVM-LD Newcomerstown, OH and take a look at what is scheduled for the next 2 weeks.
data.text:
Battle in Outer Space (1960)

When scientists suspect that an alien force is attacking Earth, they send two spaceships to weaken the enemy.

Popeye (1980)

The sailor (Robin Williams) with big forearms rows to Sweethaven and steals skinny Olive Oyl (Shelley Duvall) from large Bluto (Paul L. Smith).

Bloodline Detectives

Detectives and forensic experts recount the most extraordinary cold cases that were solved using the revolutionary technique of familial DNA testing.

The Greatest American Hero

While on a road trip through a desert, mild-mannered high school teacher Ralph Hinkley is greeted by extraterrestrials who present him with an extraordinary red flying suit that imbues him with uncanny powers.

Couples Court With the Cutlers Walker vs. Walker

A decoy tempts a Texas man and voice stress analysis is utilized.

Personal Injury Court Bennett vs. Hall

A mom sues for $150,000 in damages after she is injured assisting her daughter on a carousel ride.

Tropical Heat

A DEA agent-turned-private investigator teams up with an ambitious former travel consultant.

Loving You (1957)

A PR woman (Lizabeth Scott) and a country-music bandleader (Wendell Corey) turn a Texas truck driver (Elvis Presley) into a rock 'n' roll star.

My Dear Secretary (1948)

A playboy novelist's (Kirk Douglas) most businesslike secretary (Laraine Day) becomes his wife and literary rival.

Sherlock Holmes Faces Death (1943)

Watson (Nigel Bruce) brings in Holmes (Basil Rathbone) on a case of ritual murder at the old Musgrave estate.

It's a Great Life (1943)

Blondie (Penny Singleton) frets when Dagwood (Arthur Lake) buys a horse instead of a house.

Tropical Heat

A DEA agent-turned-private investigator teams up with an ambitious former travel consultant.

Couples Court With the Cutlers Morris vs. Rowe

A private investigator trails an aspiring Atlanta singer whose girlfriend who fears he uses his studio time as a cover to cheat with other women.

Personal Injury Court Holmes vs. Barnes & Stewart

A man sues a boat captain and a fisherman for $900,000 when a day of deep-sea fishing ends with him getting a hook in his eye.

Wiseguy

Vinnie Terranova is a brash, streetwise Italian working under cover as an agent for the Organized Crime Bureau.

Our Man Flint (1966)

Superspy Derek Flint (James Coburn), agent of Z.O.W.I.E., stops a geothermal plot to control the world's weather.
